data.name: XDrawPages
desc: gives access to a container of DrawPages or MasterPages.
The pages are stored in an index container. The order is determined by the index.
You usually get this interface if you use the XDrawPagesSupplier or the XMasterPagesSupplier at a model that contains DrawPages or MasterPages

methods.name: insertNewByIndex
desc: creates and inserts a new DrawPage or MasterPage into this container

methods.name: remove
desc: removes a DrawPage or MasterPage from this container.
